{"id":297809955,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 year, 11 months","timestamp":1580110992,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"208 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/297809955/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"53.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        set<long long int> s;\n        unordered_map<int,int> m1;\n        s.insert(1);\n        vector<int> primes({2,3,5});\n        long long int ans = -1;\n        for(int i = 1;i<=n;i++){\n            ans = *s.begin();\n            for(int x : primes ){\n                if(m1.find(ans*x) == m1.end()){\n                    s.insert(ans*x);\n                    m1[ans*x]= 1;\n                }\n            }\n            s.erase(*s.begin());\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii"}
